{"tid":2422708,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"終審法院三名海外非常任法官延任三年","createTime":"2021-02-25T11:29:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T13:49:57.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"67c5e9d2baab27f0afb07d647143395b9ca90adc","tid":2422708,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:29:49.000Z","msg":"​終審法院非常任法官任期延續<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n下稿代司法機構發出：<br />\n <br />\n  行政長官已接納終審法院首席法官的建議，將三位終審法院其他普通法適用地區非常任法官的任期由二○二一年三月一日起，延續三年︰<br />\n <br />\n  紀立信法官<br />\n  廖柏嘉勳爵<br />\n  華學佳勳爵<br />\n <br />\n  《香港終審法院條例》規定設有一份非常任香港法官及一份其他普通法適用地區法官的名單。非常任法官的任期為三年，而行政長官可根據終審法院首席法官的建議，將非常任法官的任期延續一次或一次以上，每次續期為三年。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2021年2月25日（星期四）<br />\n香港時間17時00分<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202102/25/P2021022500210.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202102%2F25%2FP2021022500210.htm&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFTnF0ojDccr9OXaUhyJR%2F0g%3D&h=adc5e862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202102/25/P2021022500210.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e5b95f765462159203009f9b134d4b972579193d","tid":2422708,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:30:57.000Z","msg":"外國勢力"},{"pid":"27752a53fc6e94c01a87b6d8126d234812249b47","tid":2422708,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:31:44.000Z","msg":"班鬼佬一定要接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ff77fe3b9435764ce4c12e2eb8b168f0ca1ccd","tid":2422708,"uid":33028,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"27752a53fc6e94c01a87b6d8126d234812249b47","tid":2422708,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:31:44.000Z","msg":"班鬼佬一定要接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T11:33:21.000Z","msg":"唔辭職咪即係接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class